                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for strengthening refining effect through RH (Ruhrstahl Heraeus) composite hydrogen blowing",
                    "一种通过RH复合吹氢来强化精炼效果的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for strengthening the refining effect through RH composite hydrogen blowing, and relates to the technical field of ferrous metallurgy. The method for strengthening the refining effect through RH composite hydrogen blowing comprises the following steps that in the RH refining process, hydrogen is blown into an ascending pipe to replace argon to serve as lifting gas, and hydrogen is blown into molten steel from at least one of the bottom and the side face of a vacuum tank; and in the later stage of RH refining, hydrogen blown into the ascending pipe is switched into argon for circular refining, and argon is blown into the molten steel from at least one of the side face and the bottom of the vacuum tank. Through composite hydrogen blowing, composite argon blowing and vacuum treatment in RH refining, carbon, nitrogen, sulfur, hydrogen and inclusions can be deeply and synergistically removed, ultralow oxygen content control is carried out, meanwhile, addition of a deoxidizing agent and generation of a large amount of inclusions are reduced, and the device is simple in structure improvement mode, easy to operate, low in production cost, high in efficiency and suitable for industrial production. And industrial large-scale production, popularization and application are facilitated."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种通过RH复合吹氢来强化精炼效果的方法，涉及钢铁冶金的技术领域。所述通过RH复合吹氢来强化精炼效果的方法如下所示：RH精炼过程中，在上升管吹入氢气代替氩气作为提升气体，并在真空罐底部和侧面中的至少一个部位向钢液吹入氢气；RH精炼后期，将上升管吹入氢气切换为氩气进行循环精炼，并在真空罐侧面和底部中的至少一个部位向钢液吹入氩气。本发明通过在RH精炼中的复合吹氢、复合吹氩和真空处理，能够深度协同去除碳、氮、硫、氢和夹杂物，并进行超低氧含量控制，同时降低了脱氧剂的添加和夹杂物的大量生成，装置结构改进方式简单，操作简单，生产成本低，效率高，利于工业大规模生产和推广使用。"
                }
            ]
